All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
GoFo
A GoFo object is the base of the system, it contains all the users and playgrounds stored in the system and allows for signing up and logging in to a certain account
Main  
Player
A Player object is a User that can show available playgrounds and book the playground that he wants
Playground
A Playground object contains information and methods to be applied to playgrounds and relate them to their owners.
PlaygroundOwner
A PlaygroundOwner object is a User that can own Playgrounds and show their current bookings
TimeSlot
A TimeSlot object hold the information and methods of a time slot using the date (day, month, year) and hour.
User
A User class is an abstract class used to make generalization for Players and Playground Owners in the system.
